值得一提的是，山景邨內的[[Y型大廈|Y型大廈]]，在建成時主要用於接收受興建[[香港城市大學|城大校舍]]影響的木屋居民，並接收部分[[大窩口邨|大窩口邨]]重建的受影響居民<ref>{{cite new|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BakvA8rFW5EiNLmhYP3sVw&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=25&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20verbatim_dc.collection%3A%28%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22%29%20%29%20AND+%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc|title=大窩口邨重建順利 第三期明夏可落成 屆時將提供約二千個出租單位|date=1987-06-25|work=華僑日報|accessdate=2022-01-21|archive-date=2022-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121133643/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv5%2BakvA8rFW5EiNLmhYP3sVw&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=25&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=(%20verbatim_dc.collection:(%22Old%5C%20HK%5C%20Newspapers%22)%20)%20AND+(%20(%20allTermsMandatory:(true)%20OR+all_dc.title:(%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8)%20OR+all_dc.creator:(%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8)%20OR+all_dc.contributor:(%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8)%20OR+all_dc.subject:(%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8)%20OR+fulltext:(%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8)%20OR+all_dc.description:(%E7%9F%B3%E7%B1%AC%E9%82%A8)%20)%20)&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=dc.publicationdate_bsort&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc}}</ref>；另外所有Y型大廈中的景安及景樂樓3樓設有行人天橋通往社區康樂大樓。

===設施===
